tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I've been visiting Dr Shraddha since the time she newly starred practice..I have now relocated to Blore, yet  I make it a point to get all my dental treatments done with her every time I come to Mumbai. I trust her implicitly. She cares for people as a priority. She's ******* *** confident. She can be trusted to give honest opinions and she goes out of her way to make patients comfortable. Most of her patients are the elderly and she's so good with them. She understands their fears and accomodates their frailty. 
God bless the work of her hands.
The review is for those who read honest reviews and then make an informed opinion. I would go to her again and again. It started with one person in our family going to see her. Now three families in my circle (including extended family members) visit her regularly. My husband also times his annual dental visit during our Mumbai Stopovers. Just want to drive home a point, that is, when we find value in someone we take trouble to continue that relation..it's so valuable!
